
sudo chown guest cpu.txt	--> make guest own cpu.txt
or sudo chown 1001 cpu.txt	--> using userId, +1001 if theres a similar user named 1001

sudo chown guest:daemon cpu.txt	  --> setting both user and group ownership
sudo chgrp daemon cpu.txt	---> changing group to daemon
sudo chown :daemon cpu.txt   --> same effect

sudo chown -R joe:joe ~		--> recursively


